window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>One man with a device to control time, a team of hot pirate ladies, and his gun. Will it be enough to save us all? </b></p> <p>He thought he defeated the man working against him to change time, but it turns out the plot was much larger all along. This isn't about simply changing time for personal gain.</p> <p>What is it really all about? Frank can't wait to find out. He was a simple college kid, but now? He's on his way to becoming a god.</p>"; 
